{"tid":1272127,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"示威者金紫荊廣場掛「黑區旗」 特區區旗被「下半旗」","createTime":"2019-07-01T09:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T10:16:11.000Z","uid":66271,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4d3a3d7dbf82bb8ea1de26308f25c4806162391d","tid":1272127,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/07/20190701_PO_%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F07%2F20190701_PO_%25E4%25B8%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-1.jpg&h=33f3a97b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》引起社會極大爭議。  不少示威者今早圖突破警方防線，到灣仔金紫荊廣場阻礙升旗儀式，與警方一度爆發衝突。示威者中午時分再到金紫荊廣場，懸掛黑色的特區區旗，並將旁邊的紅色特區區旗下半旗，哀悼先後墮樓的反對修例示威者。<br />\n<br />\n警方嚴厲譴責今早7時半有大批示威者衝擊警方防線，警方於是進行驅散行動。警方表示，今早約9時30分，示威者向警員投擲懷疑含有不知名液體的物件，令現場警員受傷，當中有人員呼吸困難及皮膚紅腫，共13名警員送院接受治療，案件交由有組織罪案及三合會調查科跟進。警方指13人經治理已經出院。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/07/20190701_po_%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81_7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F07%2F20190701_po_%25E4%25B8%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581_7.jpg&h=b27b9b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/07/20190701_po_%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81_5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F07%2F20190701_po_%25E4%25B8%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581_5.jpg&h=f05e9c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/07/20190701_po_%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81_8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/